Phrase: Having been saved from our predicament by unidentified collaborators, we came to another tower at the end of a long stone bridge.
Anna's mistress is trapped in this tower. If Victoria is right, Anna should have already met her mistress...

Name: Victoria
Phrase: The door has not yet opened.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: I don't see Canaria either. Is there an entrance elsewhere instead of here?

Name: Anna
Phrase: No, the lady's room is behind this door. There is another entrance on the ground, but we cannot get up to the very top.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: This voice is, Anna.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: So you're really here.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: But I still can't see her.

Name: Anna
Phrase: Thank you for coming, Victoria.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Did you see your mistress, Anna?

Name: Anna
Phrase: No. For some reason the door wouldn't open. I can't hear her answer. This has never happened to me before.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Miss Victoria. I thought you said 'this girl' has the key?

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Anna, give me the key. I will open it for you.

Name: Anna
Phrase: I'm afraid that would be difficult.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Why? Please do tell me. I want to help you.

Name: Anna
Phrase: It's my job to unlock the door from the outside. It is my mistress's job to open the door from the inside. So my Lady has to respond to me...

Name: Anna
Phrase: 'Victoria! Get out of here now!

Name: Canaria
Phrase: I won't let you get away. None of you.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Canaria!

Name: Canaria
Phrase: Keheheh, you're quite clever, aren't you? I thought you'd be a power-hungry, stupid maid, but you've got a lot more to offer than I thought. I can't believe you have the guts to give me fake keys.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: It's true that I'm a power-hungry, stupid maid, but I'm no fool like you.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: You just looked at a bunch of keys and decided they were the ones you wanted. You are like a child who thinks everything is yours. That's why you were fooled for my low-level lies. Speak for yourself, you're not clever, Canaria.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: Keheheheheheh... I like you. It's like I'm getting more and more in touch with your true self, heh?

Name: Victoria
Phrase: I would never show my true self to you. I only show my true colours when I'm alone with Lady Paddington.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: Come now, what a scary face you're making. Why can't we just get along?

Name: Victoria
Phrase: That's my line. Now you are even more insane than before. You seem to be possessed by something.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: Maybe I am. I'm not the same as I was before.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: ...You shouldn't upset me too much, okay? You're a half-elf maid who grew up in a castle in the comfort of her own home.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Is this what she really is?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Be careful. Canaria summons otherworldly objects from within her Gate. She handles a wide variety of weapons, but she is also quite physically capable.

Canaria was slowly closing in on us, her face an eerie smile as she unleashed her disastrous powers. The rain poured heavily, and the footing was bad. It was too difficult to fight our enemy on a slippery bridge heavy rain.
But we were willing to face her. We couldn't afford to relax our readiness for a fight. I signaled to Victoria, Versailles and Queensway, who were leading the way, with my eyes, 'Prepare to attack'.
...But Canaria wasn't aiming for us, the Special Steel Squad.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: Found you! There you are!

Name: Canaria
Phrase: I finally got you. My little maid, the one with the key to the tower.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Um, did I just saw a woman's shadow for a moment just now?

Name: Versailles
Phrase: I saw it. And the part where Canaria grabbed part of the shadow.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: It's Anna.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: What...?

Name: Victoria
Phrase: It's Anna! Canaria is now holding onto Anna's arm. I can't see her anymore, but Anna is definitely there.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: I can't see you, but I've definitely 'got' you. Now you can't escape, I have taken part of your body.

Name: Anna
Phrase: I'm sorry Victoria. I didn't realise it was a trap...

Name: Victoria
Phrase: She was after Anna from the beginning...

Name: Versailles
Phrase: So the reason you unleashed your magic to attack us was also to bait out Anna's presence. To catch Anna trying to help us.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: Oh my, I thought you were a stupid girl for a shana, but you're surprisingly calm in a situation like this.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: I told you from the start. My aim is to get to that Raindrop Princess, the one who is making it rain. I'm after the 'failure' who is hiding behind that door.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: If I were on a mission to assassinate you and your friends, I would have already killed some of you when I kidnapped Paddington, or just all of you. It depends on my mood.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: What are you going to do with Anna? Anna is... Anna is not even of this world anymore!

Name: Canaria
Phrase: She's going to open the door.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: You saw it, didn't you? You saw this Anna monster calling for the Raindrop Princess at the door.

Name: Anna
Phrase: It's no use. Even if you use me, the Lady will not open the door. She is already aware of your presence.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: Oh really? Then I will use you as my experiment instead. The mistress might come out of the tower if she senses you are in danger.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: What do you mean by 'experiment'?

Name: Versailles
Phrase: I have a bad feeling about this. Let's stop her, Victoria.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Of course. I've been trying to do that from the very beginning.

Name: Anna
Phrase: No! You all have to run away!

Name: Canaria
Phrase: How are you going to stop me? Can you people even see this monster?

Name: Canaria
Phrase: And if you want to stop me, it's too late. I've injected this child with my oh-so-fiery love.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Love?

Name: Canaria
Phrase: He did the same to you Train Knights, didn't he? Didn't you all want the only man who has Ricardo's blood in his veins? Feels good~ it feels so good... Uhuhuhuhu~

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: You mean Iron Injection.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Are you saying that Canaria has got the power of a Divine Child?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: If so, that would mean that she has powers comparable to those of Conductor or Islington.
There is no way that this is possible. Even if Canaria could be involved in transferring power to others, it is not such a power as that is possessed by a Divine Child.
Canaria has sold her soul to the devil. She is trying to further expand this abominable dark sky.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: I didn't sell my soul. I don't believe in souls in the first place. I'm sure you would agree if you saw what this monster you call Anna now looks like.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: Souls are created at the whim of the Giant Trees and Mist. And they are always replaceable. That's the kind of power I've got.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: The roars of a monster!

Name: Queensway
Phrase: But I can't see it. Where is...?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Don't tell me, we really can't see it...

Name: Canaria
Phrase: GAHHAHAHAHA! Poor little Anna! They said you were a demon before you even showed yourself to them~?

Name: Canaria
Phrase: Your mistress didn't come to save you. You suffered in the dungeons all by yourself.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: ...Canaria.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: What now? Short-tempered, stupid maid.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: If you call Anna a monster one more time, I won't forgive you.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: Oh?

Name: Victoria
Phrase: I keep my mistress's word to heart. 'When it's critical, stop and think.'

Name: Victoria
Phrase: I stopped and thought about it and came up with this answer.
Victoria stepped back once and picked up the hem of her skirt.
-Bombs rolled out of her skirt.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: You little bitch...

Name: Versailles
Phrase: HAAH!

Name: Canaria
Phrase: Tsk!

Name: Versailles
Phrase: I cut her! She dodged, but I hurt her!

Name: Canaria
Phrase: (She's quick... This shana's power is...?)

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Where are you looking? You are not out of striking range yet, you know?

Name: Canaria
Phrase: Damn!

Name: Queensway
Phrase: She's strong... That's the real Versailles.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: No wonder they sent just two people to survey this castle.
Taking advantage of Victoria's distraction, Versailles made the first move, leapt over the narrow stone bridge and slashed in every direction, giving Canaria no chance to counterattack.
Even Queensway, who was poised to join her, is unable to match Versailles' speed and simply watched. She is a reliable attacker, but we're unable to follow up.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: Now this is unexpected. Who are you? Why are you a knight when you are a shana? I can make you my personal knight, what do you say?

Name: Versailles
Phrase: No, thank you. The shana tribe does not take part in evil.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: That's a pity. If you were that powerful, you could have been an executive of the Resistance.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: But your lack of variation in your fighting style is a drawback. You don't have the vision to fight with your friends. You are still too weak to fight alone.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: And yes, I've got you♪

Name: Versailles
Phrase: AH!?

Name: Canaria
Phrase: Good-bye, my little swordswoman. You may be bold, but if you don't know when to pull back, you can't win against a superior opponent.
Under a series of ultra-fast attacks, Canaria grabbed Versailles' legs as she flew around her.
She then opened a Gate behind Versailles, who's dangling mid-air.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: MVersailles!

Name: Versailles
Phrase: No! Stay away!

Name: Canaria
Phrase: Enjoy the interstellar worlds, Versailles. Hell if you live, or Hell if you die?
--I won't let you!

Name: Canaria
Phrase: Wha, what is this force...? Why am I being drawn to the Gate?

Suddenly, Canaria stopped moving. She then began to walk awkwardly towards the gate, regardless of her own will. Canaria's arms and legs were flailing and she attempted to resist, but eventually she was lifted into the air and her lower body was pushed into the Gate.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Reinforcements. We can't see them, but they've brought help.

-The long-eared knight and maid!
-Please save Anna!
-And also take care of the young lady.
-Anna is only a knight because of her!

Name: Putra
Phrase: Where are these voices coming from?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: There are so many of them. Are they Anna's friends?
-The secret key is not a tool.\n-You'll figure it out.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Are these voices the ones who opened the door to the tower...?

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Don't tell me, you all are the inmates from the dungeons...

Name: Canaria
Phrase: You damned prisoners! You're all monsters and you all dare talk to me!

Name: Canaria
Phrase: SSS, You hear me carefully? Wherever and whatever you're doing, I'm going to stop you all again.

Name: Canaria
Phrase: With Ricardo dead, my job is finally easier. Don't let your guard down without me, okay? All of us extremists are CRAZY!

Name: Putra
Phrase: She disappeared...

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: But the Gate hasn't. In fact, it's getting a little bit bigger.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Miss Versailles, get away from the Gate! You're going to get caught in this!

Name: Versailles
Phrase: But Anna's still here!

Name: Queensway
Phrase: We can't help her if we can't see her! Get over here now...
--Victoria, help the young lady.\n--Then tell the mistress.

I will never forget the taste of the cake you gave me that night.\nI'm glad the last place I stole things was here.\nYour 15th birthday. I wouldn't have lived a hundred years to see a miracle like that.
Thank you for saving me. Thank you for my wonderful name.
It was an honour to serve you. I am off to war. I'll miss marching in the rain, so hopefully it will stop raining.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: She's now a monster...?
She was already not a person. The Mist must have swallowed her all up and transformed her. The lady-in-waiting, Anna, is probably nowhere to be found anymore.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: This can't be...

Name: Victoria
Phrase: I see your figure at last. Even if you had not taken on this form, the result would have been the same.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: I'll take care of your mistress. The rain will stop. She has heard your message. Behind that door.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Anna, thank you for getting us this far. Thank you for protecting my loved ones.
Victoria raised her weapon. She was ready to put Anna, who had been transformed by Canaria into a monster, to sleep.
